I HATE KIDS! | Kindergarten (Part 2)! ►► https://goo.gl/ehnpjA
BENDY AND THE INK MACHINE! ►► https://goo.gl/hNV9Ul
SUBSCRIBE for More GTLive Action! ►► http://bit.ly/1LkSBnz 

School is scary, and KINDERGARTEN is a downright terror. There are few times in life where I've been as socially anxious as on the first day of school. You hardly know anyone who isn't in your family, and then Boom! You have to meet 50 new kids in a single day! Apparently the game Kindergarten adds a whole new level of horror, and Steph and I are going to brave it together. Join us for this eery Stream!

Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►► http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
Follow us on Twitter at @MatPatGT and #GTLive
